{
  "stem": "19895.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 98.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he survived without portion of his leg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they did good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "These doctors, even with those very primitive conditions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And sometime, it was in vain and nothing good came of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, I was getting a little better in a day or two.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in that location, there was given a little more of the soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was in warmer location.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do not know exactly the other part of my story which I want to tell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That I was taken out and-- and sent out from that location, back to my unit, into the barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And again, typhoid fever, and being lice everywhere on our clothes and in our hair, the eggs of the-- of the lice was just hanging and it-- you were cutting with whatever little knife somebody could have had, to try to get rid of portions of that.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was awful-looking, every one of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and as a 16-year-old boy, I felt that my beard is somewhat growing, but long pieces of hair were hanging on me, which-- I never shaved.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and then happened one event, which I will never forget, that somebody stole something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It may have been food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said that somebody should stand up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Germans who were present there were making the investigation and show an example.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And fright and torture can-- can make people speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they said that if nobody comes forward to tell who it was who stole whatever they were looking for, then execution will come.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they will decimate this group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Which means every 10th person will be taken out and-- and shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, they did good on their words.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They started to count as we stood.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
